OCR GASNet implementation relies on the following environment variables

- Mandatory build flags

GASNET_ROOT         Path to the gasnet installation
GASNET_CONDUIT      Name of GASNet conduit to use
GASNET_TYPE         (seq|par)

- Optional build flags

GASNET_CFLAGS       Additional cflags to use when compiling the OCR GASNet comm-platform

- Mandatory run flags

PATH:               Environment PATH including ${GASNET_ROOT}/bin to use GASNet launchers
OCR_LDFLAGS:        Linking flags for OCR applications to link with GASNet libraries
